ok az miktarda elektrik y\'fck\'fc ta\'fe\'fdyan son derece k\'fc\'e7\'fck par\'e7ac\'fdklard\'fdr. I\'fe\'fdk enerjisi, klorofil ve di\'f0er \'fd\'fe\'fdk yakalayan pigmentlerdeki elektronlar\'fd iterek y\'f6r\'fcngelerinden \'e7\'fdkart\'fdr. Bu ba\'fe
